{"tid":491491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貪吃成禍！山東潮興挖食海知了　專家憂滅絕","createTime":"2017-12-06T14:36:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T12:50:11.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"211a293cd10495c4203a2330435686eca73fd2a3","tid":491491,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T14:36:10.000Z","msg":"12月06日(三) 10:08   <br />\n東網電視<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n山東青島民眾據報迷上名叫「海知了」新食物，吸引不少人組團去沙灘挖取。據相關專家稱，其學名是「解放眉足蟹」，在山東，最先發現它的地方是煙台，後來是日照，最近才在青島的海域上發現，但是過度捕獵可能引發滅絕。 <br />\n<br />\n當地早前有傳媒引述水產專家表示，「海知了」是可以放心食用的食材，報道發出後，挖食市民近期急增，大部分人都拿起大鐵鍁和水桶狂找。大多數市民都表示，第一次見到這種生物，但是對於是否需要保護，「沒有很明確的概念」。 <br />\n<br />\n專家介紹，解放眉足蟹是種介乎於蝦和蟹之間的珍貴海洋生物，連續多年「地氈式」挖掘，使得解放眉足蟹資源下降很多，日照市內已下降了70%多。解放眉足蟹與普通的對蝦、梭子蟹不同，成熟期至少要兩年，因此解放眉足蟹資源一旦被破壞，使得整個種群面臨滅絕的危險，而且它對生態環境是有修復作用的，所以盡管美味，還是建議民眾不要去採挖。"},{"pid":"31452829d84dc8bea6618d1acc771a1b3d64fe27","tid":491491,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T14:38:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171206/photo/bkncn-20171206100815468-1206_05011_001_01p.jpg?20171206104243\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171206%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20171206100815468-1206_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20171206104243&h=1de8f71f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171206/mobile/bkncn-20171206100815468-1206_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171206%2Fmobile%2Fbkncn-20171206100815468-1206_05011_001.html&d=7SLwcdWVY8Mpy4yKxH5Fd4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=3c90f4c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171206/mobile/bkncn-20171206100815468-1206_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9e382d876f000427ee3765bf325013594c3ae96b","tid":491491,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T14:39:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[img]<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171206/photo/bkncn-20171206100815468-1206_05011_001_01p.jpg?20171206104243[img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171206%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20171206100815468-1206_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20171206104243%5Bimg%5D&d=7SLwcdWVY8Mpy4yKxH5Fd4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=5b7f15de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171206/photo/bkncn-20171206100815468-1206_05011_001_01p.jpg?20171206104243[img]</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171206/mobile/bkncn-20171206100815468-1206_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171206%2Fmobile%2Fbkncn-20171206100815468-1206_05011_001.html&d=7SLwcdWVY8Mpy4yKxH5Fd4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=3c90f4c0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171206/mobile/bkncn-20171206100815468-1206_05011_001.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10c2e6dae1fab7a7ca6a22974d68dc01bf47e95","tid":491491,"uid":531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T14:40:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而且它對生態環境是有修復作用的，所以盡管美味，還是建議民眾不要去採挖。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你同蝗蟲講呢d有咩意思"},{"pid":"03efc3edc6218e4a635fd8b44b171a54f4c799ad","tid":491491,"uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T14:40:27.000Z","msg":"大陸人第一時間諗：咁要食就快，可能就黎冇得食"},{"pid":"7257c5cc96dccc89c1647fa0e18eaae4725b7980","tid":491491,"uid":30169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T14:48:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸人第一時間諗：咁要食就快，可能就黎冇得食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 垃圾特色"},{"pid":"4758a8a753fcba8a416d8833d56aff931c40b158","tid":491491,"uid":80072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T14:52:29.000Z","msg":"專食垃圾"},{"pid":"cb99ec8c120e0753c286a5aebc2d064fb2fff9c7","tid":491491,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T15:08:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a8355181fc379702943c699edea86d7a20bb27","tid":491491,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T16:11:54.000Z","msg":"支那狗放得落口既野邊會唔絕種"},{"pid":"40f2d55595fc44d9191a90752194c6cf5044e523","tid":491491,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T16:24:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b6906a91277046774c3dec7ddf8bae725531171","tid":491491,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T16:29:03.000Z","msg":"<strong>野生解放眉足蟹（Blepharipoda liberate Shen）<br />\n基本营养成分分析</strong><br />\n<br />\n侯召华 1<br />\n，宋庆武 2<br />\n，崔波 1<br />\n（1.齐鲁工业大学食品科学与工程学院，山东济南 250353）<br />\n（2.日照职业技术学院海洋工程学院，山东日照 276826）<br />\n<br />\n摘要：解放眉足蟹是一种珍稀的海产品，主产于山东日照。本文首次系统分析了解放眉足蟹的基本营养成分、脂肪酸、氨基酸<br />\n和胆固醇等理化指标，并对新鲜、煮熟、晒干及冻干样品进行了比较，为其开发利用提供理论基础。结果表明，解放眉足蟹富含粗蛋<br />\n白和灰分；干样品中氨基酸含量达 13.78&times;10-2 g/g，且 8 种必需氨基酸达 46.23%，必需氨基酸/非必需氨基酸为 0.77~0.92，表明氨基酸<br />\n营养均衡；28 种脂肪酸被确定，不饱和脂肪酸含量达到 73.90%以上，主要是多不饱和脂肪酸（40.03~49.53%），其次为单不饱和脂肪<br />\n酸（28.83~37.26%）和饱和脂肪酸（21.64~26.10%）；冻干样品脂肪酸中致动脉硬化指数（AI）和凝血指数（TI）分别为 0.93 和 0.13；<br />\n鲜样品胆固醇含量为 51.54&times;10-2~61.52&times;10-2 mg/g，干样品为 248.99&times;10-2~251.15&times;10-2 mg/g，但差异并不显著。结论：解放眉足蟹是一<br />\n种营养丰富的海产品，具有很强的开发潜力。<br />\n关键词：解放眉足蟹；理化指标；脂肪酸；氨基酸；胆固醇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當食物黎研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189a8821fd72d4d9465d6f889f48f2c06d2b04b4","tid":491491,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0391b1b8812e7aed31e193acc188d6dc926ddafd","tid":491491,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:14:25.000Z","msg":"人都係可食用，仲唔快d捉人去食？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44de171af021b59836a7e41cf8ba21eaf22decd","tid":491491,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:18:48.000Z","msg":"唔係點會叫蝗虫"},{"pid":"a8bb5063e4f89cf7da6a89f1c871f4489232260d","tid":491491,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:27:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ade6f4118ecf1769a6e5c551980c6f8048eff31","tid":491491,"uid":116289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:28:52.000Z","msg":"幾時食垃圾"},{"pid":"2d6bc43744091f711e0e4aee392329bb48c789a5","tid":491491,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:31:12.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲所到之地 寸草不生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd15e850d039e331b2e4733277bd2d4f79d8ee0","tid":491491,"uid":48964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:31:24.000Z","msg":"免費又擺得入口就咩都唔理去搶，好可怕既民族性"},{"pid":"079c600fa0f5b1c90cbb17d48aee38fe5ec324dc","tid":491491,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:25:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4915e8e9e7056e9132f6db417779042c05c7f5","tid":491491,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:27:49.000Z","msg":"香港人都係啦，就黎冇得食更加要食。"},{"pid":"2cc720fad624642d62065695a3cc2aa5666a9edb","tid":491491,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T12:50:11.000Z","msg":"解放啲咩"}]}